Title: The Super Silly Fiesta
Plot: The Big Red Chicken in hosting a Super Silly Fiesta and everyone is invited, but something is wrong, the cake for the party is missing. Upon hearing the Big Red Chicken's problem, Dora and Boots goes to the fiesta to help the Big Red Chicken find the cake for the party. In order to get to the fiesta, Dora and Boots goes through The Singing Gate, over the Troll Bridge and to The Fiesta.
